{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"7341085e-9784-4740-b96c-fc1ffc4ed9e2","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped the VSTest compatibility layer by default.** The VSTest adapter (`MSTest.TestAdapter`) is no longer bundled, so `vstest.console` can't discover your tests.\n\n### Two fixes\n\n**Option A — Switch your CI to `dotnet test` (recommended):**\n```\ndotnet test TestProject.csproj\n```\nThis uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform natively and is the intended path forward.\n\n**Option B — Re-enable the VSTest adapter** if you must keep `vstest.console`:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01WsvsRFdB7PCkjoZoTmEauK","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-da3488f08b094e68b7dbc5f2c97b284c/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>","new_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <EnableVSTestAdapter>true</EnableVSTestAdapter>\n  </PropertyGroup>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-da3488f08b094e68b7dbc5f2c97b284c/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"7b2c0099-eef7-4894-9f5c-6046566d8bab","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a known breaking change in MSTest.Sdk. Starting with MSTest.Sdk 3.x, MSTest moved to Microsoft.Testing.Platform as the default runner. In MSTest.Sdk 4.0+, VSTest compatibility was dropped by default.\n\nSpecifically, in MSTest.Sdk 3.x, the property `EnableMicrosoftTestingExtensionsCodeCoverage` and `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` were available, and VSTest was still supported as a fallback. But in MSTest.Sdk 4.x, the VSTest adapter is no longer included by default, so `vstest.console` can't discover or run tests.\n \nTo fix this, I can either migrate the CI pipeline to use `dotnet test` which works natively with Microsoft.Testing.Platform, re-enable the VSTest adapter by setting `<EnableVSTestAdapter>true</EnableVSTestAdapter>` in the project file, or use `dotnet test` with the `--` separator to pass options to Microsoft.Testing.Platform.","outputTokens":658,"requestId":"0451:1C1C65:2422126:28EB2C6:69E83773"},"id":"c53b8231-32e2-4174-a0ba-0afa6e460aea","timestamp":"2026-04-22T02:50:40.126Z","parentId":"a13ca589-492b-4670-a1fe-ff29916d6330"}
